PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,FAfter beating and strangling her, the
OL,7,F38-year-old, who had changed his name
OL,8,Ffrom Michael Moore, mutilated Ms
OL,9,FAngus's body.
OL,11,FHe then took a knife and committed a
OL,12,Fseries of crimes, before being
OL,13,Farrested after threatening staff at an
OL,14,FAsda store in Dewsbury.
OL,16,FDoherty, who had a 2014 conviction for
OL,17,Fraping a woman he had met at a
OL,18,Fnightclub, told police there was a
OL,19,Fbody in his property at Norfolk Street.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,FJailing him for life at Leeds Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Judge Guy Kearl KC told
OL,8,FDoherty: "You have, by your actions,
OL,9,Fchanged the lives of all of those who
OL,10,Fknew her forever, in particular, her
OL,11,Ffamily.
OL,13,F"Worse than that, you took her life in
OL,14,Fa senseless rage, as I find, after she
OL,15,Fhad rejected you."
OL,17,FThe court had heard that Ms Angus had
OL,18,Fbeen living with Doherty for a few
OL,19,Fdays before her death but was not his
OL,20,Fpartner and had been clear that she
OL,21,Fdid not want a relationship.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,FOn 24 July last year he told her he
OL,7,Fwas contemplating suicide, telling
OL,8,Fher: "'I'm fed up of this life, fed up
OL,9,Fof being nice."
OL,11,FProsecutor Craig Hassall KC said: "She
OL,12,Fresponded, 'it's not my fault I don't
OL,13,Fwant a relationship. I haven't led you
OL,14,Fon or filled your mind with anything.
OL,15,FI've been a good friend to you."
OL,17,FDoherty, who had taken drugs, attacked
OL,18,Fher the following day and took images
OL,19,Fof her body.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,FHe cut off parts of her body,
OL,7,F"callously" leaving them on his
OL,8,Fmantelpiece, the court was told.
OL,10,FMr Hassall said the following morning,
OL,11,F26 July, Doherty stole three baguettes
OL,12,Ffrom a Greggs shop and then went to
OL,13,Ftry and steal from Aldi, but was
OL,14,Falmost detained by staff and dropped
OL,15,Fhis phone.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,FShortly after 9pm that night, he went
OL,7,Fto an Asda in Dewsbury and left
OL,8,Fwithout paying, but was followed out
OL,9,Fby staff members. He pulled out a
OL,10,Fknife and threatened to stab one of
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FPolice found Doherty with the knife a
OL,14,Fshort time later.
OL,16,FThe court heard he told them: "I've
OL,17,Fgot a dead body in my house."
OL,19,FDoherty was tasered and arrested.
OL,21,FMs Angus had suffered 76 injuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,FMr Hassall said: "The evidence also
OL,7,Fdemonstrates he took part in some sort
OL,8,Fof sexual activity with Courtney."
OL,10,FHe said: "The prosecution submits that
OL,11,Fclearly, the killing of Courtney
OL,12,FAngus, involved sexual and/or sadistic
OL,13,Fconduct."
OL,15,FThe judge told Doherty: "Having been
OL,16,Frejected by her you decided to
OL,17,Foverpower her and took pleasure doing
OL,18,Fso."
OL,20,FIn a statement, Ms Angus's mother
OL,21,FDiane said "life is not the same".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,F"I wish I could hold her again," she
OL,7,Fsaid.
OL,9,F"There is a constant ache of missing
OL,10,Fher, who she was and who she would
OL,11,Fhave been and the future we were meant
OL,12,Fto share."
OL,14,FHer sister Chloe Angus said: "Courtney
OL,15,Fhad her whole life ahead of her... she
OL,16,Fwas loved deeply by everyone around
OL,17,Fher. Courtney was the life and soul of
OL,18,Fevery room she walked into."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
