FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780045515
OL,3,CLife sentence for rapist who murdered
OL,4,Cwoman in 'sadistic' attack
OL,6,FShe added: As a family we are learning
OL,7,Fto exist in a world that no longer has
OL,8,Fher in it and it feels unbearably
OL,9,Fempty... grief is something I carry
OL,10,Fwith me every day."
